      <p class="promise__author">— The Ferni Philosophy</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# USE CASES #}
<section class="section use-cases" id="use-cases">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Real Life</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">For the moments that matter</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">Ferni meets you where you are—whether you're navigating career decisions, processing stress, or building better habits.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="use-cases-grid reveal-stagger">
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M20 7h-9"/><path d="M14 17H5"/><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="3"/><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Career Crossroads</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Navigate job changes, salary negotiations, and that nagging feeling something needs to shift.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"I got a job offer but I'm not sure if I should leave..."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Stress & Overwhelm</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Process anxiety, talk through what's weighing on you, and find clarity in the chaos.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"I can't stop thinking about everything I need to do..."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Building Habits</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Start exercising, eat better, sleep more—with Maya's help, small changes stick.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"I keep saying I'll start tomorrow..."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Life Decisions</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Moving cities, ending relationships, taking risks—the big decisions deserve real thought.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"I don't know if this relationship is working..."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Relationships</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Navigate family dynamics, friendships, and the complicated relationships that shape us.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"My parents never seem to understand..."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M14.5 10c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5v-5c0-.83.67-1.5 1.5-1.5s1.5.67 1.5 1.5v5c0 .83-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5z"/><path d="M20.5 10H19V8.5c0-.83.67-1.5 1.5-1.5s1.5.67 1.5 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5z"/><path d="M9.5 14c.83 0 1.5.67 1.5 1.5v5c0 .83-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5S8 21.33 8 20.5v-5c0-.83.67-1.5 1.5-1.5z"/><path d="M3.5 14H5v1.5c0 .83-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5S2 16.33 2 15.5 2.67 14 3.5 14z"/><path d="M14 14.5c0-.83.67-1.5 1.5-1.5h5c.83 0 1.5.67 1.5 1.5s-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5h-5c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5z"/><path d="M15.5 19H14v1.5c0 .83.67 1.5 1.5 1.5s1.5-.67 1.5-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5-1.5z"/><path d="M10 9.5C10 8.67 9.33 8 8.5 8h-5C2.67 8 2 8.67 2 9.5S2.67 11 3.5 11h5c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5z"/><path d="M8.5 5H10V3.5C10 2.67 9.33 2 8.5 2S7 2.67 7 3.5 7.67 5 8.5 5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="use-case__title">Daily Check-ins</h3>
        <p class="use-case__description">Start your day with intention, end it with reflection. Build self-awareness over time.</p>
        <p class="use-case__example">"I just need someone to talk through my day..."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# TEAM #}
<section class="section" id="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Meet Your Team</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">Six specialists. One conversation.</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">Each brings unique expertise. Ferni coordinates them seamlessly based on what you need.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="team-grid reveal-stagger">
      {% for member in site.team %}
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="persona-avatar persona-avatar--lg persona-avatar--{{ member.id }}">
        <div class="persona-avatar__ring"></div>
        <div class="persona-avatar__orb">
          <span class="persona-avatar__text">{{ member.initials }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
        <h3 class="team-card__name">{{ member.name }}</h3>
        <p class="team-card__role">{{ member.role }}</p>
        <p class="team-card__bio">{{ member.bio }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# HOW IT WORKS #}
<section class="section how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Getting Started</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">Three ways to connect</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">No downloads. No accounts required. Start talking in seconds.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="steps reveal-stagger">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">1</div>
        <div class="step__content">
          <div class="step__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="step__title">Call</h3>
          <p class="step__description">Dial <strong>{{ site.phone }}</strong> from any phone. No app needed. Just talk naturally like you would with a friend.</p>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" class="step__link">Call now →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">2</div>
        <div class="step__content">
          <div class="step__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="step__title">Text</h3>
          <p class="step__description">Send a message to the same number. Perfect for quiet moments or when you need to organize your thoughts first.</p>
          <a href="sms:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" class="step__link">Send a text →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">3</div>
        <div class="step__content">
          <div class="step__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="step__title">Web App</h3>
          <p class="step__description">Open the app on any device. Voice, text, or video—your choice. See your history and track progress.</p>
          <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}" class="step__link">Open app →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

