{# FAQ #}
<section class="section faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Questions</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">Frequently asked</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-list reveal-stagger">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">Is Ferni a replacement for therapy?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>No. Ferni is a life coaching companion, not a licensed therapist. We're great for day-to-day support, goal-setting, habit building, and talking through decisions. For clinical mental health needs, please work with a licensed professional. Ferni can complement therapy, but not replace it.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">How does the phone call feature work?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>Just call {{ site.phone }} from any phone—no app needed. Your conversation is linked to your phone number, so Ferni remembers you. It's like calling a friend who actually picks up. Works on any phone, anywhere in the world.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">What does "infinite memory" mean?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>Unlike other AI, Ferni remembers every conversation you've had. Mention something months ago? Ferni recalls it. This creates continuity—like talking to a friend who actually knows your story, your goals, and what you've been through.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">Is my data private and secure?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>Absolutely. Your conversations are encrypted and never sold or shared. You can export or delete your data anytime. We're building trust systems, not advertising systems. Your privacy is fundamental to how we operate.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">Who are the 6 specialists?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>Meet the team: <strong>Ferni</strong> (Life Coach & Coordinator), <strong>Peter</strong> (Research & Deep Dives), <strong>Alex</strong> (Communication & Expression), <strong>Maya</strong> (Habits & Routines), <strong>Jordan</strong> (Planning & Organization), and <strong>Nayan</strong> (Wisdom & Perspective - Partner tier). Ferni connects you to the right specialist based on what you need.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">Can I cancel anytime?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>Yes, no contracts, no commitment. Cancel with one click. Your free tier access continues even if you cancel a paid plan. We want you to stay because Ferni helps, not because you're locked in.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__question">What makes Ferni different from ChatGPT?</summary>
        <div class="faq-item__answer">
          <p>ChatGPT is a general-purpose AI. Ferni is purpose-built for life coaching with specialized personas, infinite memory of your conversations, voice-first interaction (just call!), and a relationship that deepens over time. It's the difference between a search engine and a friend.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

